title: United Kingdom Imports of Lead & Related Articles
description: Imports of Lead & Related Articles in the United Kingdom increased to 37.42 GBP Million in September from 5.78 GBP Million in August of 2022. Imports of Lead & Related Articles in the United Kingdom averaged 23.80 GBP Million from 2000 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 89.94 GBP Million in March of 2022 and a record low of 0.38 GBP Million in February of 2022. This page includes a chart with historical data for the United Kingdom Imports of Lead & Related Articles.
author: Hm Customs And Excise
